s-greg-abel-warren-buffett-successor-charlie-munger-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreg%20Abel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20a%20vice%20chair%20at%20the%20company%2C%20take%20over%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20has%20remained%20an%20enduring%20force%20as%20an%20investor%20and%20businessman%20for%20decades.%20He%20purchased%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20in%201965%20as%20a%20New%20England%20textile%20mill%20and%20transformed%20it%20into%20a%20%241%20trillion%20conglomerate%20that%20spans%20multiple%20industries.%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20owns%20companies%20like%20Geico%2C%20Dairy%20Queen%2C%20and%20Fruit%20of%20the%20Loom%2C%20and%20has%20been%20a%20major%20investor%20in%20companies%20like%20Apple%20and%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Buffett's%20announcement%2C%20business%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20shared%20tributes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483ab3aa-58f3-4c3a-ada8-835b8eece69e%5C%22%3ETim%20Cook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Apple%20CEO%20praised%20Buffett%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20never%20been%20someone%20like%20Warren%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20one%20of%20the%20great%20privileges%20of%20my%20life%20to%20know%20him.%20And%20there's%20no%20question%20that%20Warren%20is%20leaving%20Berkshire%20in%20great%20hands%20with%20Greg.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed214d46-8d65-494b-bf13-3647badd6b31%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dimon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20a%20fixture%20of%20Wall%20Street%2C%20praised%20Buffett%20in%20a%20message%20after%20the%20investor's%20big%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWarren%20Buffett%20represents%20everything%20that%20is%20good%20about%20American%20capitalism%20and%20America%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20investing%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20nation%20and%20its%20businesses%20with%20integrity%2C%20optimism%2C%20and%20common%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20per%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BI've%20learned%20so%20much%20from%20him%20to%20this%20very%20day%2C%20and%20I%20am%20honored%20to%20call%20him%20a%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22311d0e5a-573c-4960-b2eb-03f4881ccf13%5C%22%3EBill%20Gross%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20investor%20and%20PIMCO%20cofounder%20Bill%20Gross%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email%20that%20Buffett's%20vision%20set%20him%20apart%20from%20other%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20vision%20was%20not%20limited%20to%20an%20optimistic%20vision%20of%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Gross%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThrough%20his%20insurance%20holdings%20that%20by%20their%20structure%20allowed%20for%20the%20investment%20of%20premiums%20at%20a%20near%20zero%20cost%20into%20higher%20returning%20assets%20such%20as%20Coke%2C%20AMEX%20and%20Apple%20and%20in%20so%20doing%20he%20created%20a%20spread%20which%20over%20time%20lead%20to%20billions%20and%20the%20recognition%20not%20just%20as%20a%20stock%20picker%20but%20as%20a%20financial%20structural%20wizard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20also%20congratulated%20Buffett%20and%20recalled%20on%20X%20the%20first%20time%20his%20firm%20gave%20Berkshire%20one%20of%20its%20first%20loans%20in%20the%20mid%20'70s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20nothing%20about%20insurance%20and%20candy%20stores%20but%20was%20sold%20by%20his%20long-term%20vision%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Gross%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BCongratulations%20my%20friend%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20on%20the%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20but%20on%20the%20philanthropy%20and%20the%20years.%20Having%20a%20cherry%20Coke%20with%20you%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20my%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ebe8872-c654-4907-95f0-4753b58ef144%5C%22%3EMark%20Cuban%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Buffett%20was%20his%20%26quot%3Binvesting%20hero%26quot%3B%20and%20shared%20a%20photo%20of%20him%20with%20the%20investing%20legend%20at%20a%20Dairy%20Queen%20in%20Omaha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20go%20to%20DQ%20in%20Omaha%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20my%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcement%2C%20Cuban%20also%20reposted%20on%20X%20a%20video%20showing%20Buffett%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20during%20the%20annual%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac214ced-c19e-46ed-8e06-9ae680227427%5C%22%3ESpencer%20Hakimian%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHakimian%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Tolou%20Capital%20Management%2C%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20X%20of%20Buffett%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20from%20the%20crowd%20at%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20annual%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurtain%20call%20for%20the%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20Hakimian%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e86526e3-f66d-4459-996e-7c6220b8e9f7%5C%22%3ERon%20Olson%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOlson%2C%20a%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20board%20member%2C%20told%20CNBC%20that%20Buffett%20has%20%26quot%3Blived%20a%20life%20full%20of%20surprises.%20Very%20few%20of%20his%20decisions%20have%20been%20anything%20but%20sensational.%20I%20am%20very%20anxious%20to%20see%20Warren%20become%20the%20Charlie%20Munger%20for%20Greg%20Abel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlson%20also%20believed%20Abel%20%26quot%3Bis%20ready%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20doubt%20about%20that.%20We've%20known%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e09b0da-11e7-477b-a0eb-55b8cb86ded3%5C%22%3EFrench%20Hill%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arkansas%20GOP%20congressman%20and%20former%20businessman%20told%20CNBC%20that%20Buffett%2C%20Abel%2C%20and%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20board%20%26quot%3Bhave%20done%20a%20magnificent%20job%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20preparing%20shareholders%20for%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20added%20that