's%20board%20of%20directors%20will%20ultimately%20decide%20on%20his%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20and%20shareholders%20expect%20that%20if%20Abel%20does%20assume%20the%20role%2C%20he%20will%20maintain%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20investment%20philosophy.%20He%20told%20shareholders%20at%20this%20weekend's%20meeting%20that%20he%20would%20start%20by%20maintaining%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bfortress%20of%20a%20balance%20sheet%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20allows%20it%20to%20make%20large%20investments%20without%20relying%20on%20banks%2C%20Barron's%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbel%20is%20known%2C%20however%2C%20for%20having%20a%20more%20hands-on%20management%20style%20than%20Buffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20estimated%20by%20Forbes%20to%20be%20worth%20%24484%20million%20in%202021.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20sold%20his%201%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20Energy%20unit%20for%20%24870%20million.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbel%20has%20risen%20through%20the%20ranks%20with%20a%20persistent%20focus%20on%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20native%20played%20hockey%20in%20his%20early%20years%20and%20attended%20the%20University%20of%20Alberta.%20He%20graduated%20in%201984%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20PwC%20after%20graduation%20and%20quickly%20moved%20on%20to%20a%20small%20company%20called%20CalEnergy.%20In%201999%2C%20CalEnergy%20acquired%20MidAmerican%20Energy%20and%20adopted%20its%20name.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20bought%20a%20controlling%20interest%20in%20MidAmerican%20Energy.%20Abel%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20MidAmerican%20in%202008%20%E2%80%94%20renamed%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20Energy%20in%202014%20%E2%80%94%20and%20helmed%20it%20until%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20served%20on%20the%20board%20of%20several%20major%20companies%2C%20including%20Kraft%20Heinz%2C%20and%20has%20been%20affiliated%20with%20organizations%20and%20institutions%20like%20the%2