child's%20cup%20was%20empty%2C%20they'd%20fill%20it%20with%20water.%20They%20were%20so%20good%20with%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20also%20amazing%20with%20parents.%20If%20one%20of%20the%20parents%20had%20an%20empty%20glass%20of%20prosecco%2C%20the%20two%20babysitters%20offered%20to%20top%20up%20their%20drinks.%20They'd%20see%20me%20offering%20food%20or%20drinks%2C%20and%20they%20would%20do%20the%20same%20without%20being%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20I%20could%20have%20paid%20a%20catering%20company%20to%20do%20similar%20tasks%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20known%20if%20they'd%20be%20comfortable%20or%20capable%20around%20kids.%20It%20was%20also%20much%20cheaper%20to%20hire%20babysitters%20than%20caterers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20also%20cheaper%20to%20hire%20babysitters%20than%20to%20hire%20a%20photographer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20party%2C%20both%20babysitters%20took%20photographs%20of%20all%20the%20fun.%20I'd%20previously%20priced%20up%20a%20photographer%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20taking%20pictures%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20enjoy%20the%20moment.%20A%20professional%20photographer%20would%20have%20cost%20twice%20the%20price%20for%20half%20the%20hours.%20The%20photos%20they%20both%20took%20were%20incredible%20too.%20They%20captured%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282616e3c-8fa8-4f5a-b4a2-1cbabd5eb132%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20enjoy%20the%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20party%2C%20people%20asked%20who%20the%20babysitters%20were%2C%20commenting%20on%20how%20delightful%20and%20helpful%20they%20were.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20so%20much%20help%2C%20I%20could%20relax%20and%20enjoy%20the%20party%20more%20than%20if%20they%20hadn't%20been%20there.%20All%20the%20pressure%20w