e%20Fortune%20500s%20and%20professional%20services%20firms%2C%20founders%20of%20private%20equity%20and%20private%20credit%20firms%2C%20institutional%20investors%20at%20the%20CIO%20level%20of%20pension%20funds%2C%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds%2C%20family%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20are%20those%20who%20serve%20them.%20That%20could%20be%20chief%20marketing%20officers%20and%20chief%20communications%20officers%20or%20heads%20of%20investor%20relations%20who%20are%20supporting%20their%20CEOs%20or%20founders%20at%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolicy%20makers%20and%20politicians%20who%20care%20deeply%20about%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20central%20banking%20systems%20globally%20will%20be%20in%20tow%20too.%20This%20is%20high-level%20crowd%20geared%20around%20investing%2C%20deal-making%2C%20and%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22187ff254-440e-4d3f-b258-cff5d911877d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20miss%20the%20health%20panels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20cancer%20survivor%20and%20major%20health%20philanthropist%2C%20Michael%20Milken%20surrounds%20himself%20with%20the%20best%20minds%20in%20finance%2C%20and%20also%20in%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20know%20what%20is%20possible%20today%20with%20genetics%2C%20cancer%20care%2C%20Alzheimer's%20treatments%2C%20GLP-1s%2C%20preventative%20medicine%2C%20healthy%20aging%2C%20or%20the%20positive%20effects%20of%20psychedelics%2C%20the%20health%20content%20sessions%20are%20a%20must.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20owe%20Michael%20Milken%20the%20healthiest%20version%20of%20myself%20because%20I%20attended%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Live%20to%20a%20Healthy%20100%26quot%3B%20panel%20almost%20ten%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226be90b9a-7cb3-469a-9819-52bce3494a73%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20the%20private%20party%20circuit%20very%20seriously%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20the%20most%20valuable%20part%20of%20the%20conference%20is%20what%20is%20not%20on%20the%20agenda.%20There%20is%20a%20healthy%20party%20circuit%20around%20the%20Milken%20conference%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20best%20events%20are%20at%20private%20homes%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%20during%20the%20evenings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20events%20are%20not%20publicized%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20be%20a%20longtime%20attendee%20to%20know%20what's%20happening%20when%20and%20where.%20My%20advice%20is%20to%20buddy%20up%20with%20a%20conference%20vet%20and%20ask%20for%20help%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20private%20event%20circuit.%20Or%20hire%20a%20firm%20that%20is%20in%20the%20know%20to%20%26quot%3Bconcierge%26quot%3B%20your%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20my%20favorite%20private%20events%20have%20been%20Goldman%20Sachs's%20women's%20lunch%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BWheelhouse%26quot%3B%20event%20at%20Bette%20Davis's%20former%20party%20house%2C%20and%20dinner%20at%20Dan%20Loeb's%20home%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Third%20Point.%20If%20you%20don't%20maximize%20this%20aspect%20of%20the%20conference%2C%20you%20get%20only%20half%20the%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bae14b5-3764-4c8b-8aef-91d463aafb5c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20be%20afraid%20to%20approach%20people%20in%20the%20hallway%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20inch%20of%20the%20Milken%20conference%20is%20filled%20with%20someone%20you%20should%20get%20to%20know.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20people%20are%20easy%20to%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20memories%20at%20Milken%20happened%2010%20years%20ago%20when%20my%20business%20was%20still%20relatively%20small.%20I%20ran%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-rubenstein-book-warren-buffett-carlyle-berkshire-key-investing-skills-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Rubenstein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20co-founder%20and%20co-chairman%20of%20Carlyle%20Group%2C%20in%20the%20hallway%20and%20had%20a%20ten-minute%20conversation%2C%20during%20which%20he%20spent%20most%