hhole%20Kulche%20So%20Much%2C%20I%20Quit%20My%20Job%20to%20Build%20a%20Vending%20Machine%20That%20Serves%20Them%20in%2060%20Seconds%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20failures%2C%20but%20I%20realised%20that%20if%20I%20hang%20around%20long%20enough%2C%20I%20will%20see%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sagar%20Malhotra%2C%20a%20banker-turned-entrepreneur%2C%20who%20has%20become%20a%20viral%20sensation%20in%20the%20food%20industry%20because%20of%20his%20innovation.%20His%20journey%20sets%20an%20example%20of%20how%20persistence%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20passion%20for%20what%20you%20love%2C%20can%20push%20you%20to%20achieve%20anything%20in%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20spending%20over%20a%20decade%20in%20a%20well-established%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F420808%2Fvijay-pratap-indian-mountaineering-adventhrill-dehradun%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20banking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20your%20way%20up%20to%20the%20position%20of%20Vice%20President%20at%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20but%20feeling%20that%20something%20was%20still%20missing.%20That%20was%20the%2039-year-old%20banker%E2%80%99s%20dilemma.%20While%20he%20had%20everything%20many%20would%20envy%2C%20there%20was%20one%20thing%20that%20tugged%20at%20his%20heart%20%E2%80%94%20his%20undying%20craving%20for%20the%20authentic%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spiced%20chickpeas%20served%20with%20soft%20leavened%20flatbread)%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Sagar%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20secure%20career%20to%20pursue%20a%20project%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20sure%20about.%20Motivated%20by%20his%20love%20for%20food%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20passion%20into%20a%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20started%20with%20my%20desire%20to%20bring%20the%20authentic%20taste%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20That%20one%20thought%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Vice%20President%20to%20building%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Janakpuri%2C%20West%20Delhi%2C%20Sagar%20always%20had%20an%20unshakable%20love%20for%20food%2C%20especially%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20his%20hometown.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20staple.%20But%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20could%20never%20find%20the%20same%20authentic%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remembers.%20The%20craving%20for%20that%20delicious%20and%20spicy%20%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20left%20him.%20He%20would%20often%20wonder%20why%20North%20India%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20food%20is%20not%20available%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%2014%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20prestigious%20banks%20like%20Citibank%20and%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20steadily%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%20Even%20though%20he%20was%20fond%20of%20his%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20shake%20off%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20of%20his%20own.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20during%20a%20senior%20management%20programme%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%202023%20that%20I%20met%20people%20who%20were%20doing%20things%20beyond%20their%20regular%20jobs%2C