Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20how%20a%20vendor%20would%20make%20it%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20with%20the%20consistency%20of%20a%20machine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20fresh%20ingredients%20every%20day%2C%20and%20nothing%20is%20stored%20overnight.%20The%20chickpeas%20are%20boiled%20fresh%20in%20our%20kitchen%20every%20morning%2C%20and%20the%20machine%20is%20cleaned%20and%20loaded%20with%20fresh%20ingredients%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulchas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20grilled%20manually%2C%20but%20Sagar%20is%20already%20working%20on%20the%20next%20version%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20which%20will%20bake%20them%20too%2C%20making%20the%20entire%20process%20fully%20automated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20it%20to%20be%20easy%20and%20convenient%20for%20my%20customers.%20Everything%20should%20come%20from%20the%20machine%2C%20both%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulcha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chakh%20De%20Chole%20is%20open%20from%2010%20am%20to%205%20pm%20every%20day%20to%20serve%20customers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T180553.458_11zon-1746189362-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChakh%20De%20Chole%20is%20open%20from%2010%20am%20to%205%20pm%20every%20day%20to%20serve%20customers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20if%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%3F%20What%20if%20I%20fail%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20discussing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F285107%2Fengineer-couple-builds-electric-bull-for-farm-maintenance-work-help-marginalised-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20of%20building%20a%20machine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20juggling%20time%20as%20a%20full-time%20banker%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20shares%20the%20countless%20moments%20of%20doubt%20and%20failure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20build%20a%20vending%20machine.%20There%20were%20times%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20if%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%3F%20What%20if%20I%20fail%3F%E2%80%99%20But%20I%20kept%20pushing%20forward%20and%20got%20motivated%20by%20little%20wins%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20learn%20everything%20from%20scratch%2C%20and%20it%20was%20ex