al%20insight%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20strong%20industry%20perspective%20to%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20automotive%20industry%2C%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20real%20fascination%20for%20innovations%20in%20battery%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sameer.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20what%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20team%20through%20our%20flagship%20initiative%2C%20the%20MG%20Motors%20Developer%20Program.%20My%20background%20in%20vehicle%20efficiency%20management%20allowed%20me%20to%20help%20benchmark%20the%20device%20against%20global%20standards%20right%20from%20the%20early%20stages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20role%20focused%20particularly%20on%20data%20acquisition%20systems%20and%20ensuring%20the%20device%20met%20the%20evolving%20demands%20of%20the%20EV%20ecosystem.%20%E2%80%9COur%20team%20worked%20closely%20on%20designing%20and%20refining%20how%20the%20device%20collects%20and%20interprets%20data%2C%20while%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20team%20constantly%20updated%20the%20AI%20models%20based%20on%20our%20input%20and%20user%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubham%20conducts%20demonstrations%20of%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20for%20dealers%20so%20they%20know%20the%20benefits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031